Privacy Policy
Hover provides 3D property data and other services. This Privacy Policy is intended to help you understand what personal information we collect, how we use and share that information, and how you can make choices regarding your personal information. The Policy applies to all services provided or powered by Hover, including websites, mobile applications, co-branded or white-labled sites and apps, and products that are integrated into third-party apps and sites, like embedded 3D visualizers and design tools.
